entries.title_d: You've been given orders from Garett to deliver a notice, explaining to the contacts at Jabba's Star that an attack is imminent and that you need their support.
entries.title: Tatoo System: Transfer the Notice
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast1 Hutt Informant:\#pcontrast3 < So far so good. I've been informed that our war vessels are ready. Escort the commander safely to the waypoint I've given you. We'll get this attack underway with his help. >
entries.quest_rendezvous2_t: Meet with contact at Jabba's Star
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: At Jabba's Star, easily found in the datapad under the POI tab, you'll need to meet with the designated contact and transfer the attack notice.
entries.quest_location_d: Travel to the Tatoo System and complete your mission.
entries.quest_dock2_d: To dock with the contact, use the /dock command.
entries.hello_d: Let's git this over wit'. I can feel Valari'ns close.
entries.found_loc_d: I'm sending you the location at which you'll meet our contact. You need to transfer the notice once you get there and after the contact arrives.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Let's git this here notice of yeh. We don't want Valari'ns gettin' yeh anymore.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Yeh done good, pilot. There may be room in our ranks fer folks like yeh. Carry on.
entries.arrived_at_delivery: It pleases me that you made it to Jabba's Star safely. Our contact will arrive soon.
